{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/dashboard/layout,_N_T_/dashboard/page,_N_T_/dashboard"}},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><!--_M2vSVkNQMMT50lt4FHtc--><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/d13ffc8efd6b932f.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-2eb758dea75faf50.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/4bd1b696-c023c6e3521b1417.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/255-38b49df12a94ee57.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-356c8beca43b27b0.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/373-7d96024889cb4733.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/dashboard/page-7842eed1d4fea56b.js\" async=\"\"></script><title>Assign — Your AI Tutor</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"The AI tutor that actually teaches you. Not just gives you answers.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" type=\"image/x-icon\" sizes=\"16x16\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><main class=\"min-h-screen bg-background text-foreground\"><nav class=\"flex justify-between items-center px-10 py-5 border-b-2 border-foreground\"><a href=\"/\" class=\"flex items-center gap-2 no-underline\"><span class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary inline-block\"></span><span class=\"font-mono text-lg font-medium text-foreground tracking-tight\">assign</span></a><div class=\"flex items-center gap-5\"><a href=\"/progress\" class=\"font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground no-underline hover:text-primary transition-colors\">progress</a><a href=\"/notes\" class=\"font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground no-underline hover:text-primary transition-colors\">notes</a><span class=\"font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground\"></span><button class=\"brutalist-shadow-hover font-mono text-xs border-2 border-foreground px-4 py-2 bg-background text-foreground cursor-pointer\">sign out</button></div></nav><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-10 py-14\"><div class=\"mb-14\"><h1 class=\"text-6xl leading-tight tracking-tight text-foreground\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Instrument Serif&#x27;, serif;font-style:italic\">what do you want<br/><span class=\"text-primary\">to learn today?</span></h1></div><section class=\"mb-16\"><p class=\"font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-widest mb-5\">choose a mode</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-4 gap-4\"><a href=\"/trek/new\" class=\"brutalist-shadow brutalist-shadow-hover block border-2 border-foreground bg-card p-6 no-underline\"><div class=\"text-3xl mb-4\">🗺️</div><div class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xl text-foreground mb-1 uppercase tracking-tight\">trek</div><div class=\"font-mono text-xs text-primary mb-3\">learn it end to end.</div><div class=\"font-sans text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Adaptive trek now runs through the B2C teaching loop with notes and progress tracking.</div></a><a href=\"/spark\" class=\"brutalist-shadow brutalist-shadow-hover block border-2 border-foreground bg-card p-6 no-underline\"><div class=\"text-3xl mb-4\">⚡</div><div class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xl text-foreground mb-1 uppercase tracking-tight\">spark</div><div class=\"font-mono text-xs text-primary mb-3\">stuck on one thing?</div><div class=\"font-sans text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Drop in one topic. AI finds exactly what you don&#x27;t know and fixes only that — fast.</div></a><a href=\"/recall\" class=\"brutalist-shadow brutalist-shadow-hover block border-2 border-foreground bg-card p-6 no-underline\"><div class=\"text-3xl mb-4\">🧠</div><div class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xl text-foreground mb-1 uppercase tracking-tight\">recall</div><div class=\"font-mono text-xs text-primary mb-3\">prove you know it.</div><div class=\"font-sans text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Explain a topic from scratch. AI listens, then tells you exactly what broke down.</div></a><a href=\"/build\" class=\"brutalist-shadow brutalist-shadow-hover block border-2 border-foreground bg-card p-6 no-underline\"><div class=\"text-3xl mb-4\">🔨</div><div class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xl text-foreground mb-1 uppercase tracking-tight\">build</div><div class=\"font-mono text-xs text-primary mb-3\">figure it out yourself.</div><div class=\"font-sans text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Pair programmer that never writes code for you. It asks until you get there.</div></a></div></section><section><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center mb-5\"><p class=\"font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-widest\">your trek courses</p><a href=\"/trek/new\" class=\"font-mono text-xs text-foreground border-b border-foreground pb-px no-underline hover:text-primary transition-colors\">+ new course</a></div><div class=\"py-20 text-center font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground\">loading...</div></section></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-2eb758dea75faf50.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[9766,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n3:I[8924,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n4:I[1959,[],\\\"ClientPageRoot\\\"]\\n5:I[116,[\\\"373\\\",\\\"static/chunks/373-7d96024889cb4733.js\\\",\\\"105\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/dashboard/page-7842eed1d4fea56b.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n8:I[4431,[],\\\"OutletBoundary\\\"]\\na:I[5278,[],\\\"AsyncMetadataOutlet\\\"]\\nc:I[4431,[],\\\"ViewportBoundary\\\"]\\ne:I[4431,[],\\\"MetadataBoundary\\\"]\\nf:\\\"$Sreact.suspense\\\"\\n11:I[7150,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/css/d13ffc8efd6b932f.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n\